WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Decades ago, communication was fairly limited.

2
00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:08.000
There used to be little effective communication over long distances.

3
00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:14.000
However, technological advancement has made it possible in instant time.

4
00:00:15.100 --> 00:00:18.000
Technology hasn't affected just communication.

5
00:00:18.200 --> 00:00:23.000
Online shopping allows for deliveries to be made efficiently while offering a range of products.

6
00:00:23.200 --> 00:00:25.400
Education can take place online with widely accessible knowledge.

7
00:00:26.200 --> 00:00:28.500
We can order food, a basic necessity, with a few clicks!

8
00:00:28.900 --> 00:00:31.000
Technology has also changed our culture.

9
00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:36.500
It has become the medium for entertainment and engagement.

10
00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:40.000
In addition, it connects many with lifestyle, fashion, and beauty.

11
00:00:40.500 --> 00:00:46.500
Asides from sharing knowledge, it is a creative outlet for creators to share their content.

12
00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:49.100
During these challenging times of quarantine,

13
00:00:49.500 --> 00:00:49.100
it has connected distanced communities through digital screens.

14
00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:55.000
Technology has managed to be a safe space and be our medium of self expression.

15
00:00:55.100 --> 00:00:57.000
Thank you for watching!